channel.title: MangOH Red - Net Signal Impedances
channel.description:
Hello,
I wanted to ask about the Layer Impedance table that comes with Mangoh red Gerber files (File attached). Do we have a list of signal nets using these impedance profiles?
I saw there was already this question but I have an urgent project and wanted to see if I could get a quicker answer. If there is a number we could instead utilize to ask about this, we would be very grateful.
Thank you!
